{"tid":1043132,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"（純呻）自己工連屋企人請既看護不如就好大壓力覺得自己好無用","createTime":"2019-03-02T04:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T08:34:03.000Z","uid":180913,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c7cdb8a348f21b9c728e55586c36f5eb252d3771","tid":1043132,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:55:57.000Z","msg":"而加係某港島私家醫院獨立病房，<br />\n屋企人就請左個私人看護照顧老人家。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己就好似廢人一樣，成個屋企得我一個無價值咁，得我一個唔係大學生。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前11月做完手術都意識到自己開始年紀都大，都唔可以再做hea工就轉工同ot。同埋計住自己洗錢，轉食呆飯，拎屋企d 人哋送禮嘅coupon黎慳住洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n但我可以點？<br />\n再努力轉工返pt都係月入唔過兩萬衰過同期同學，唔好話同班親戚比。<br />\n<br />\n讀書唔得  ，搵錢唔得  ，我完全搵唔到出路去keep住屋企人現時生活水平。<br />\n2-3日醫院費就係我成個月人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都唔敢話我返咩工搵幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個思緒好混亂，諗到之後條路 一片灰暗咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔打住，屋企人叫出去食lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終於唔使食呆飯慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個post純呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇下有冇同路人（屋企期望同能力不相符）既人傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食飯先 88<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788e2abc58c436caae103563e2221937127fb0db","tid":1043132,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b95da02e84550de5ea8764c3791518de420d5d67","tid":1043132,"uid":90820,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:58:30.000Z","msg":"睇標題都唔知樓主想噏乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n內容又一嚿嚿咁<br />\n樓主食完飯執執篇文先再出過啦"},{"pid":"1a4de6ae23b7bb12f4656e735b7dfc37128b81cf","tid":1043132,"uid":90820,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"788e2abc58c436caae103563e2221937127fb0db","tid":1043132,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:59:08.000Z","msg":"呢篇文連肥絲都唔知從何入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7b55a32d504eac6df5bd0b68aeff94a55c3181","tid":1043132,"uid":52912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:59:13.000Z","msg":"等屋企養囉<br />\n投下資<br />\n你做一世都唔會搵到你屋企有既錢"},{"pid":"a66eab69d01c52b2fa565cecdaa35bbc30fcd540","tid":1043132,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:59:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4ce7b7324cf226b58ae7535fc4c04dcc9e518ad","tid":1043132,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:00:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13f34235bd28698a1969d919fc5889ace5811eb0","tid":1043132,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b95da02e84550de5ea8764c3791518de420d5d67","tid":1043132,"uid":90820,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:58:30.000Z","msg":"睇標題都唔知樓主想噏乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n內容又一嚿嚿咁<br />\n樓主食完飯執執篇文先再出過啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:00:13.000Z","msg":"係啊，無對過 ，食完飯返黎執一執<br />\n附近好多好野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2228fecd39c2c801cd8b7215e186345b3f61752e","tid":1043132,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:00:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98bb6ff640db25cdda781d43c20308deb04ba002","tid":1043132,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":2,"scor